(2) The Registration Committee shall consist of the following members: (a) the Vice-President ; (b) the Honorary-Secretary ; (c) two Past Presidents and fully paid up corporate members of the Institute ; (d) the Chairperson of the Membership Committee; and (e) a senior Corporate Member nominated by the President and approved by the Council .
